This project is a website aimed for user who don't want to spend too much money at lunch time.

Midipascher.fr allows you to find restaurants whose menus fit in your "ticket restaurant".

Midipascher.fr allows you to answer that familiar question : 'what will we have for lunch today?' at lower cost.

The website is written in java, aimed to run on a servlet container.

It allows a restaurant manager to register its restaurant, update restaurant informations, unregister restaurant
It allows a site admin to create/update/delete restaurant
It allows a site admin to create/update/delete reference data
It allows any visitor to find a restaurant based on geo informations.
It allows any visitor to save its searches.
It allows any visitor to be informed with registering pricing


Have fun on midipascher.fr
